From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Rune Lillesveen <futhark@chromium.org>
Date: Thu, 21 May 2026 02:31:22 -0700
Subject: Missing reattach of CSSStyleDeclaration for some @-rules

@position-try, @property, and @counter-style did not reattach their
CSSStyleDeclaration CSSOM wrapper when reattaching the rule.

Also, @position-try did not clone its property set as necessary which
resulted in modifying a shared property set between stylesheet when the
StyleSheetContents is shared.

@property does not have this issue since it is fully immutable.

@counter-style only creates a wrapper for internal devtools usage, but
still needs its cloning fixed.

Removed Copy() methods which were not in use.

Bug: 514445398, 514906337
Change-Id: Id0abdb9013332e6f84ce6ebaa7ad13af75529451
Reviewed-on: https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/7865527
Reviewed-by: Steinar H Gunderson <sesse@chromium.org>
Commit-Queue: Rune Lillesveen <futhark@chromium.org>
Cr-Commit-Position: refs/heads/main@{#1634136}

